Module cz.cvut.fel.pjv.dd_simple_tool
Package cz.cvut.fel.pjv.dd_simple_tool

Class RightPanelGame

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.pjv.dd_simple_tool.RightPanelGame
public class RightPanelGame
extends java.lang.Object
VBox showing ListView of objects that can be added to map within the Game window. Objects are sorted into 8 different tabs, after selecting a tab, contents are displayed in the ListView below. 9. tab "Maps" opens a window showing map saves, which can be loaded into the game. Below ListView is "Give panel" where user can input some values to adjust the stats of currently selected player. Below "Give panel" are showed currently selected objects.
